{"tid":1469354,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"前線好清楚自己做緊乜！","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:32:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:51:00.000Z","uid":176753,"like":8,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1917d9160f0b1381774bcfbfe801f1f7b32202c4","tid":1469354,"uid":176753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:32:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">喂！其實目標好撚清晰！</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>攬炒！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">攬炒意思係乜？<br />\n係爭取 美國 取消香港獨立關稅區！<br />\n從而話俾全世界知一國兩制已死，美國帶頭不承認一國兩制！<br />\n美國佬講到明，要出解放軍先會考慮取消香港獨立關稅區！<br />\n你地醒未？唔升級點出解放軍？機場靜坐就出解放軍？<br />\n稍微行動升級左少少，就話做得唔好，不割蓆。客觀效果就係割蓆！口講不割蓆，其實就係割蓆！<br />\n姐係依家攬炒，大家有幾層樓係手啦，唔捨得係咪？<br />\n唔捨得香港經濟崩潰係咪？<br />\n反送中運動至今，超過800人被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到最後，大家都係自私嘅！抗爭梗係人地犧牲，自己收割啦！<br />\n最好就無痛抗爭！有錢又有自由～</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>隨便鬧我分化！我依家就係分化！恥與為伍！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每次睇到手足保釋出黎周身傷！<br />\n睇到被爆眼女救護，再睇睇機場班潔癖撚和理非，<br />\n真係好心痛！心痛已經犧牲嘅人！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>而剩下的一啲覺悟都冇！<br />\n香港人，真的不配擁有民主！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"503da489c93d9924cff1ce8fd2b405f6d3c092fc","tid":1469354,"uid":23672,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:33:01.000Z","msg":"攬炒 係對隊同你一齊炒<br />\n尋晚係我地自炒"},{"pid":"48b6e0b421aa3be5ef5c65be2445dcdf4b8a11b0","tid":1469354,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:33:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0223a4d87f6928d18f0be17b243706ac8ea56904","tid":1469354,"uid":239663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:34:15.000Z","msg":"攬炒你應該放火燒政總炸機場, 咁就出硬解放軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74356803e2d2e6a4fe233200875f1acad594745c","tid":1469354,"uid":161125,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0223a4d87f6928d18f0be17b243706ac8ea56904","tid":1469354,"uid":239663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:34:15.000Z","msg":"攬炒你應該放火燒政總炸機場, 咁就出硬解放軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:35:28.000Z","msg":"去石崗放火咪得囉, 要攬炒呀嗎。<br />\n去乜9機場呀?"},{"pid":"c7bf0bb9797e5cfce1d2095d196d03079d2bdc51","tid":1469354,"uid":283083,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"503da489c93d9924cff1ce8fd2b405f6d3c092fc","tid":1469354,"uid":23672,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:33:01.000Z","msg":"攬炒 係對隊同你一齊炒<br />\n尋晚係我地自炒"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:35:51.000Z","msg":"同遊客攬炒左<br />\n政府開心到開香檳"},{"pid":"56422db9e566d1c2880b5ffb9145b26454bfad14","tid":1469354,"uid":176753,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c7bf0bb9797e5cfce1d2095d196d03079d2bdc51","tid":1469354,"uid":283083,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"503da489c93d9924cff1ce8fd2b405f6d3c092fc","tid":1469354,"uid":23672,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:33:01.000Z","msg":"攬炒 係對隊同你一齊炒<br />\n尋晚係我地自炒"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:35:51.000Z","msg":"同遊客攬炒左<br />\n政府開心到開香檳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:38:39.000Z","msg":"有邊次升級不割蓆？<br />\n為琴晚嘅事道歉好容易<br />\n問題係搞邊度不割蓆？<br />\n次次都反對架啦！"},{"pid":"d20c9aa3efaabcb13173b19e7775fef69a274964","tid":1469354,"uid":67813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:39:25.000Z","msg":"有冇留意，一直以來親建制都係極團結的。<br />\n你先唔好理佢哋嘅團結係唔係為咗利益，<br />\n係唔係冇自由意志，<br />\n總之佢哋就係好團結。<br />\n甚至乎佢哋嘅成功，就係源於團結。<br />\n你見佢哋其實係甚少會公開批評同路建制仔。<br />\n(有時都會嘅，但比起嚟真係好少)<br />\n好似何姓元朗大總統啲行為咁癲，<br />\n好多親建制中產暗地裏可能都唔認同佢，<br />\n但佢哋冇公開叫佢應該點、唔應該點。<br />\n佢哋最能體現到咩叫不篤灰不割蓆。"},{"pid":"a6a89ea82bb75eab5ce2227e3fcfb26c0158d833","tid":1469354,"uid":262035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:40:25.000Z","msg":"攬炒既原意係敵損1000，自損300都無問題<br />\n依家敵人無損無爛，自己就損哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e528603d5632af9181509e3c4cba37198cbcbc3","tid":1469354,"uid":298428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:40:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">而家人地冇事 <br />\n但前線隨時俾人當恐佈分子槍弊<br />\n<br />\n人地冇事呀<br />\n我地自己抄左咋</span>"},{"pid":"bee5721ef9d12011dc44ac5e90fce2086c1808ca","tid":1469354,"uid":160074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:42:34.000Z","msg":"勇武嘅前線們，橫眉冷對千夫指，俯首甘為孺子牛。從來只有暴政，沒有暴徒，感謝勇武前線日以繼夜以命相博 ，方令暴政黑警不致對我們任意妄為，勇武派願意為我們擋子彈，那現在勇武派將面臨巨大的輿論壓力，你們會為他們擋嗎？"},{"pid":"6ad405a241b1f09